BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:ADkRWgvvrM_CZBsa96duG
SUMMARY:Maye & Ambar Lucid
DTSTAMP:20260317T215402Z
DTSTART:20260504T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:maye and Ambar Lucid come together for a joint tour that celebr
	ates emotional honesty\, cultural duality\, and the power of intimacy on s
	tage.Born in Venezuela and based in the US\, maye has built a devoted glob
	al following through deeply personal songwriting that blends Latin roots\,
	 indie pop\, and alternative soul. Her music feels diaristic yet expansive
	\, anchored by vulnerability\, warmth\, and a voice that invites listeners
	 inward rather than pushing outward.Ambar Lucid\, a Mexican-Dominican arti
	st raised between cultures\, brings a hypnotic\, cinematic presence that f
	uses psychedelic pop\, dreamlike visuals\, and bilingual storytelling. Her
	 work explores identity\, intuition\, and self-discovery\, pairing etherea
	l production with striking lyricism that resonates across borders.Together
	\, maye and Ambar Lucid create a shared live experience that feels intimat
	e\, immersive\, and emotionally charged. This tour is not about spectacle 
	for spectacles sake\, but about connection. Two artists\, two worlds\, and
	 one space where language\, culture\, and feeling dissolve into something 
	singular and unforgettable.\nAll sales are final. There are no refunds unl
	ess the event is cancelled or postponed Opening Acts are subject to change
	 or cancelation at any time without notice. No refund will be owed if an O
	pening Act is changed or canceled. Doors times subject to change Tickets m
	ay not be resold or offered for resale. If we suspect tickets have been pu
	rchased for resale purposes only\, we reserve the right to void or cancel 
	the tickets without refund. Tickets obtained from unauthorized sources may
	 be invalid\, lost\, stolen or counterfeit and if so\, are void.\nPrice: $
	0 - $0\n\nhttps://www.ticketweb.com/event/maye-ambar-lucid-the-crocodile-t
	ickets/14108114\n\nFrom The Crocodile
URL:https://www.ticketweb.com/event/maye-ambar-lucid-the-crocodile-tickets/
	14108114
LOCATION:The Crocodile\, 2505 1st Ave\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:crocodile-main
