BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:fqLSrR2x9bDhvHnDxn1jI
SUMMARY:Mariel Buckley\, guests
DTSTAMP:20260317T215403Z
DTSTART:20260629T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Advance: $20 ($26.27 after fees)\n\nDay of: $25 ($31.42 after f
	ees)\n\nMariel Buckley:\n\nUnapologetically genuine\, wry and soft-hearted
	\, Mariel Buckley has planted her flag firmly as a songwriter who’s in it 
	for the long haul. She aims to find herself squarely on the fringes and ex
	actly where she belongs: singing and writing songs for the underdogs. Rais
	ed in the heart of Canada’s rodeo and country music scenes\, she was desti
	ned to challenge the boundaries around her\, both in life and in song. Wit
	h a fearless spirit that’s consistently broken through both genre and pers
	onal barriers\, Buckley’s unique blend of angst-driven alt-folk has made h
	er a standout artist\, offering a fresh and dynamic perspective on modern 
	Americana music.\n\nPlease note\, the Sunset Tavern is a strictly 21+ bar 
	and venue and does not accept vertical ID’s for entry.\n\nhttps://link.dic
	e.fm/v563f7306146\n\nFrom Sunset Tavern
URL:https://link.dice.fm/v563f7306146
LOCATION:5433 Ballard Avenue Northwest\, Seattle\, Washington 98107\, Unite
	d States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:sunset-tavern
CATEGORIES:Sunset Tavern
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
